questions.quote: Jerry, how come you didn't say hello to me the other day, huh?!
I guess it would be nice if you called all the ticket holders if the game was going to be rained out.
That's it. What you want one George? I can get one for you. No problem. Jerry, you want one? They're delicious. My pleasure.
Oh I can't believe-- why don't you get rid of that piece of junk.
It's right in the explosion scene. So if you could just...leave me a little window. You know, my, uh, my aunt had a thing removed with a laser. All right, I don't want to interrupt your meal, so...
I just got here, Ma! I'd like to spend a little time with you.
Anyway ... So John told me that Richie is in town from Los Angeles and he's really messed up on drugs. So I told him that he should do an intervention.
Uh, well, listen. I feel really horrible about trying to keep you two apart and I just wanted to apologize.
Oh, I can't believe you're dropping out, too. So now Kramer and I have to pay for the entire gift?
Hey Kramer, my parents are gonna have to move back to Florida, isn't that great?
